<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="impression-n">impression <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ɪm'preʃn/    美 /ɪm'preʃn/  </p>
<p>[C]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>印记；压痕</strong></h4>
<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>印象；感觉：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He <strong>left / made</strong> a deep <strong>impression on</strong> me. / He left me with a deep impression<strong> left me with</strong<strong>impression_2</strong>
他给我留下了深刻的印象。</p><footer>2015 江苏改</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I <strong>had the impression (that)</strong> we had met before.
我感觉我们以前见过。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">派生词汇</h2>
<p>impressionist /ɪm'preʃənɪst/ n  [C]  </p>
<h2 id="_3">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>My <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ (第一印象) of him was that he was a kind and thoughtful young man. 
  （2012 山东改）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. first impression  </p></div>